ver consumer virtual reality the company has offices in new york japan and the uk and is the current market leader for video eyewearcitation needed forte was a pioneer during the mids developing immersive head mounted displays for virtual reality and video gaming applications in  the company was hired as a subcontractor to raytheon designing display electronics for a digital night vision weapon sight in  the vfx headgear was featured in a commemorative us postal service stamp collection celebrating the s the vfx was replaced by a higher resolution system dubbed the vfxd in mid  in  vuzix launched its first consumer electronics product the icom personal internet browser in  vuzix provided a custom high resolution handheld display system that created the d imagery for hitachis pavilion at the  worldâs fair in aichi japan the hitachi pavilion allowed users to interact with computer generated models and dioramas of endangered species in a mixed reality ride in  the company changed its name to icuiti later that year icuiti launched its first product designed specifically for consumers the v video eyewear also in  icuiti was awarded its first military rd contract to develop a high resolution monocular display device for viewing tactical maps and video this development would lead to the taceye product line which began rate production in  and is currently used in many major military programs including the battlefield air operations kit a rebranding in  changed the companys name from icuiti to vuzix in  vuzix introduced the first production model seethrough augmented reality glasses the star  it was released in august  for  vuzix is currentlywhen under contract with darpa to design and build a next generation heads up display for military ground personnel the darpa pcas program is large rd program with the goal of allowing the joint tactical air controller the ability to rapidly engage multiple moving and simultaneous targets within his area of responsibility in january  at ces vuzix corporation demonstrated working models of its new m smart glasses the official press event of ces rated as one of the five top gadgets expected at ces by cnbc and given the ces innovations award the vuzix smart glasses m expected to ship in second half of  will enable wearers to access data and content from an ios or android smart phone from the cloud and âhands freeâ the m was officially released in december  for  double the original announced price in january  intel invested  million in the company gaining  ownership of the company  innovationsedit video eyewareedit vuzix created the first video eyewear to support stereoscopic d for the playstation  and xbox  augmented reality eyewareedit vuzix ar augmentedreality smartglasses  the most advanced ar tech on citation needed vuzix created the first commercially produced passthrough augmented reality headset the wrap ar the wrap ar has two vga video displays and two cameras that work together to provide the user a view of the world which blends real world inputs and computer generated data during the consumer electronic show in  vuzix announced the raptyr the raptyr is a seethrough augmented reality display prototype that will be the first consumer product of its kind when it reaches the market in needs update the star  is the first seethrough augmented reality display to be massproduced and was scheduled to be released in august needs update the vuzix smart glasses m are scheduled for commercial release in late  sweet vuzix describes the m as the worldâs first commercially available hands free display and cloud connected communications system the vuzix m contains a virtual display with integrated camera and powerful processing engine running the android os  users will be able to connect wirelessly to their smartphone androidbased or other compatible devices the m is also powerful enough to connect directly to the internet run applications and games itself when connected to a smartphone users will be able to engage with existing and future applications such texts video email mapping and audio as a hands free accessory with integrated cameradisplay functionality vuzi smart glasses will let users answer the phone with a visual address book and enable applications from text messaging and email to visual navigation via an integrated gps and head tracker along with more advanced features like video recording the interactive head tracking and integrated hd camera combined with applications on the m and a smartphone linked to the cloud empower smartphone based augmented reality applications referencesedit  about vuzix corporationÂ   augmented reality edges closer to the mainstream  cnet newsÂ   the best new technology  oprahcomÂ   vuzix and ns solutions corporation partner to deliver augmented reality solutions for manufacturingÂ   us navy buys into smart glasses trend in deal with vuzix venturebeat retrieved Â   intel acquires  stake in vuzix a maker of smart eyewear  kitguru wwwkitgurunet retrieved Â   forte vfx headgear virtualreality system museum of interesting techÂ   celebrate the century  s  no  of   us postal service  Â   unofficial vfxd page stereodcomÂ   hendricks veronica icom personal internet browser iappliancewebcom retrieved Â   nature contact  hitachi group pavilions ubiquitous entertainment ride expororjpÂ   vr interfaces icuiti v virtualworldletsnetÂ   ndia briefpdf ndia brief check url value help pdf retrieved Â   httpwwwprnewswirecomnewsreleasesicuitichangesnametovuzixcorporationhtml  vuzix star  headset augments your reality not your bank account engadgetcom aol techÂ   vuzix star  price and release date for augmentedreality glassesÂ   shachtman noah  darpas holograms rain hell wiredcom  danger room retrieved  june Â   persistent close air support defense advanced research projects agency retrieved  june Â   five hot gadgets expected at ces  january Â   ces innovation awards january Â   vuzixs androidpowered m smart glasses now available to preo